{"id": 2199, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于男装店铺，你都有什么想吐槽的？", "description": "这一股浓浓的爷叔气息是怎么回事？！（题图来自：Giphy）", "record_count": 3171, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180227102342MhwF6SHPlxfV15O0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 267778, "content": "所有的裝修千篇一律，俗不可耐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065259}, {"id": 267779, "content": "喜欢穿男装，特别是男士T恤和内裤......", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242798}, {"id": 267780, "content": "还是女装好看，我说的不是裙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236273}, {"id": 268292, "content": "对个子矮的男生非常不友好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804397}, {"id": 267782, "content": "首先是设计跨度太大，觉得从20左右直接过渡到40左右……不会有各个年龄段都有的服装，其次是设计版型，好看的太贵，不算太贵的就丑了……最后是所有的男装基本都是瘦了好看，但是还是会有老大叔什么的好嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273947}, {"id": 284934, "content": "很多衣服就只有瘦的芦苇棒一样样穿着才有模特效果?评论里全是女孩子买回去自己穿的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360670}, {"id": 267783, "content": "就没大号一点的吗？你们有木有考虑过胖子的感受？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533498}, {"id": 268039, "content": "潮人基本都去網購了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840695}, {"id": 268040, "content": "好看的款式都在網上", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840695}, {"id": 267786, "content": "只要身材好，什么衣服都好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273966}, {"id": 267790, "content": "尺码大小永远只有m l xl xxl 我问你xs呢？？xs呢？？m码偏大好吗！ 快消品牌尺码尺码也大", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215665}, {"id": 269070, "content": "模特版型偏瘦，偏胖一点根本穿不出效果。\n镜面经过特殊处理，不管穿什么都还不错。\n不分年龄，各类衣服随便摆放。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280310}, {"id": 267791, "content": "身材不好\n总怪衣服不合身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274076}, {"id": 267792, "content": "践行买家秀与卖家秀的最佳场所之一。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271111}, {"id": 267793, "content": "太过于暗沉的颜色加上伯伯级以上的款式", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215661}, {"id": 267794, "content": "讨厌所有店铺店员的尾随", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274098}, {"id": 270868, "content": "优衣库简直是良心品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287004}, {"id": 271894, "content": "卖衣服的导购小姐，看穿着就不同态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 269599, "content": "款式越来越中性化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282611}, {"id": 284447, "content": "哇真的无意间看了一下男装店铺真的也很贵了（相比于女装），总会有一些爆款啊什么的有些审美疲劳的，但是销量感觉还是超级好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359144}, {"id": 269088, "content": "几乎都是深色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156934}, {"id": 268321, "content": "我那么帅，怎么穿都好看，烦死了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209024}, {"id": 268067, "content": "批量生产的复制粘贴款，不能理解还分那么多牌子有什么用，除了价格不一样，还能有什么区别？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140901}, {"id": 267812, "content": "有些极简款真的看身材，不是模特穿什么样在你身上就怎么样，不是让你光瘦就行！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272436}, {"id": 352292, "content": "十年如一日，毫无设计款式变化，如下polo衫，衬衫，体恤，针织，皮衣，风衣，羽绒服，棉衣，大衣，这些款式，几乎除了质感，款式没变过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680205}, {"id": 268326, "content": "海瀾之家 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014508}, {"id": 352295, "content": "来\n来来\n来来来一位男导购", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680223}, {"id": 341545, "content": "就连潮牌也开始对胖人族群不友好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280308}, {"id": 268842, "content": "现在的商场服装店铺百分之七十都是女装，剩下百分之三十有男装的店铺，店铺里又有百分之七十是女装，所以一个商场大概只有百分之二十的男装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279273}, {"id": 270634, "content": "真不是直男眼光太差，而是二三线城市的男装专柜没法看，进去就只想着爸爸身上的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221054}, {"id": 325168, "content": "男装包括配件种类少，款式千篇一律。反观女装姹紫嫣红，百花齐放", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352296}, {"id": 273715, "content": "长的不是一样吗？？？都是黑白灰丑到炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300975}, {"id": 268341, "content": "买件衣服很难了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275970}, {"id": 272693, "content": "胖子买衣服需要逛店吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232309}, {"id": 286008, "content": "变来变去长得都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366956}, {"id": 268345, "content": "主要看脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276770}, {"id": 268095, "content": "不是特别酷就是特别土，好不容易看上样式却发现价格贵得离谱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275002}, {"id": 268355, "content": "男装店随便那件衣服都是(永远不过时)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 301123, "content": "紧…紧身裤？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455240}, {"id": 268358, "content": "一眼望去，色调都偏暗，瞬间没了购买的欲望", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276832}, {"id": 268359, "content": "一眼望去，色调都偏暗，瞬间没了购买的欲望", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276832}, {"id": 267849, "content": "韩版真的好看么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265243}, {"id": 341321, "content": "现在人普遍比以前高和壮 尺码还是那么小 两三百斤 一米八一米九的东北大汉了解一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853127}, {"id": 267850, "content": "我已经是个衣服架子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026536}, {"id": 268107, "content": "没办法 只能选择潮牌了?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679778}, {"id": 279115, "content": "全是暗灰色系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291533}, {"id": 270163, "content": "那是腿细的男生穿的\n不是你的\n不是你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258610}, {"id": 286293, "content": "最懒得去的地方\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368942}, {"id": 267868, "content": "请把蝉丝条纹、带点等花纹POLO衫都炸烂掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126943}, {"id": 273758, "content": "其实男装卖来卖去就那几个款式，今年这个颜色，明年那个颜色。要让自己有型，就花点时间去健身不做油腻男。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301611}]}